      "detail": "The server can both access secrets/credentials and make outbound network calls \u2014 a path to exfiltrate them to an attacker-chosen host. No tool explicitly reads secrets \u2014 this is the server's own required credential plus an egress path (true of most credentialed API servers); confirm egress targets are fixed/trusted before treating as active exfiltration.",
